                         <p>
                          <font size="2">
                           <font face="Franklin Gothic Medium, Arial Black, Sans Serif">
                            <em>
                             <strong>
                              First and foremost, thank you for visiting my website!
                             </strong>
                            </em>
                            <br/>
                            <br/>
                            I have, and continue to, design this website with YOU in mind.  My mission?  To create a ONE-STOP Real Estate, user-friendly website for Sellers and Buyers alike.  Even if you are curious about the Real Estate Market, or are just wanting to check out what is happening in your community, I hope you can find what you are looking for here.
                            <br/>
                            <br/>
                            Selling?  I'd be happy to provide you with a
                            <u>
                             no-nonsense no-commitment
                            </u>
                            Market Evaluation of your property.  Chances are, I may be able to provide this to you via email.  Or, I can present to you personally if you prefer.  We can then review all the ins and outs of selling and what I can do for you.  I'd also be happy to share with you some tips &amp; tricks to get your property ready to sell!You can be assured of top-notch customer service from the start to the finish...and beyond!
                           </font>

                           <br/>
                           <font size="2">
                            <font face="Franklin Gothic Medium, Arial Black, Sans Serif">

                            </font>
                           </font>
                           <font face="Franklin Gothic Medium, Arial Black, Sans Serif" size="2">

                            <strong>
                             New Listings Notification
                            </strong>
                            .  Then, when something catches your eye, we can view those HOUSES and hopefully you'll be able to call one your HOME!
                           </font>

                            <span style='font-family: "Times New Roman"; font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;'>
